  "slug": "what-does-my-body-want-me-to-know-today-journal",
  "title": "What Does My Body Want Me to Know Today?",
  "subtitle": "A journal prompt set for listening to the body rather than pushing past it",
  "excerpt": "A journal prompt set for the habit of overriding physical signals. Asks the body directly what it is communicating, and what responding to that signal would actually require.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from the Day 1 body-listening prompt in WEIGHT LOSS: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025).",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A journal prompt set for the habit of treating the body's signals as problems to manage rather than information to read. These prompts ask what the body is saying before you decide what to do about it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to journal prompts? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "journal prompts as practice",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/journal-prompts-as-practice"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Warm-up",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "How does my body feel right now, today?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Not how you think it should feel. What it actually feels like at this moment. Write a short, direct description.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where in my body is there the most sensation right now?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Name the location. What kind of sensation is it?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Closer in",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "If this sensation could speak, what would it say?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Write it in first person. Let the sensation tell you what it needs.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Is there something the body has been asking for that I have been putting off?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Rest. Movement. Food. Warmth. Fresh air. Quiet. Name it.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 4
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "What is one small thing I could give the body today in response to what it told me?",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Not a full lifestyle change. One thing, today.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Where this practice comes from",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Adapted from the Day 1 body-listening prompt in WEIGHT LOSS: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025). The Day 1 idea is simple. Change starts from listening to where you are, not from making yourself be somewhere else.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
